BESS WELLS JANNEY, as Administratrix of the Estate of Mabel H. Wade, deceased, v. JAMES M. SWAIN, JR. 19 So. (2nd) 612

June Term, 1944

November 10, 1944 Division A C. B. Peeler, for appellant. George E. Turner, for appellee. *148PER CURIAM:

From a careful study of the record and briefs we are unable to find reversible error in the judgment and record and the judgment is affirmed.

BUFORD,. C. J., TERRELL, CHAPMAN and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
